text: Surrounded by private estates. 1 HDB block, 1 market, 1 hawker centre & 1 MSCP collectively named Empress Mall. Nice peaceful breezy place.

This place provides the basic necessities for the residents here. 2 GP clinics 1 pet Vet clinic, 2 fruits stalls/shop, 1 Hardware store,a 711,a butchery/meat shop,2 provision shops,2 coffee places,1 laundry shop& lastly 2 hair salons.

Empress market with shops .
Fresh vegetables & bouquet flowers available from 6:00am to 12:00noon.
There is kopitam.
Tailors available for mending clothes.
Fruit shop, bakery everything available
Veterinary doctor,human doctor

Although more popular with it's soya sauce chicken rice and noodle, the char siew or barbeque pork is excellent. The char siew I ate this morning were succulent, fragrant and generous, big thick pieces.
Get you weekly marketing, meats, fruits and dry stores. A good clinic and a few pet veterinarians. Or try your luck at Singapore pools.
